    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. It's been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Everything is in pristine shape, and it drives like a dream. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
