      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty\u2014it is honestly in absolutely incredible shape. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feel to it! If you're looking for something that\u2019s been kept in pristine condition, this is the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! \u2728",
