    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a flawless, recently serviced VANOS system and has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure absolute structural integrity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with original Sachs dampers and OEM bushings, offering the tactile steering feedback these cars are known for. The exterior retains its deep factory luster, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather and an unblemished dash. Documented valve adjustments and a comprehensive service history make this a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
